DITECH FINANCIAL, LLC, a Foreign Limited Liability Company, Appellant,
v.
RH KIDS, LLC, a Nevada Limited Liability Company, Respondent. No. 75339 Supreme Court of Nevada. FILED NOVEMBER 26, 2018

Wright, Finlay & Zak, LLP/Las Vegas

Hong & Hong

ORDER DISMISSING APPEAL

Pursuant to the stipulation of the parties, and cause appearing, this appeal is dismissed. The parties shall bear their own costs and attorney fees. NRAP 42(b).

It is so ORDERED.
